timeline.bodyText:
Written like this, it seems like a bug that || is not &&. I'd like it more like this:
if (containsPlan(v1Plans, servicePlanName)) {
     return v1Plans;
}
if (containsPlan(v2Plans, servicePlanName)) {
    return v2Plans;
}
return v1Plans;

That way it's clear that v1Plans is the default.

